## Service Patterns

### Dependency Injection

```typescript
export function createMyService(
  api: OrchestratorAPI,
  deps: {
    assignmentService: TaskAssignmentService;
    registry: AgentRegistry;
  }
): MyService {
  const { assignmentService, registry } = deps;
